    "description": "Excavations in 2025 rediscovered the Sanctuary of Apollo at Frangissa that had been previously excavated by Max Ohnefalsch-Richter. Located in a remote valley near the ancient site of Tamassos, the site produced evidence for more than 100 votive statues.",
